{
  "stem": "13096.1",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was, you know, there were a fire.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the nearest place where this, you know, the captain, he asked the permission to the Italian people, and they came, all the Jewish people to stay in the island until the ship was-- it was fixed or they-- they send another ship for it or something like that.",
      "word_count": 49
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So when this ship was sent to collect all these people, many of our-- of our young people, they joined them.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They-- when they arrived, when they arrived, you know, there were 1,500 refugees, you know, from Europe.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "When they left, there were more than 2,500 of our-- of our-- of our people joined them to go to Palestine.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Did your family ever try to leave?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because-- because we were little bit well off, you see, better off than many families.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never-- for instance, during the war, everybody was starving and this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As-- as I say, we had a little bit-- our condition economically was a little bit above, and we had money to survive even with a black market.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We thought that the war was going to finish.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We never thought that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If we knew that was happening, it was in store, we were going to go even by, you know, swimming to wherever.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, except my sister that she survived with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The governor was at the time, you know, it was De Vecchi.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "De Vecchi, you know, I don't know if you know the history.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was one of the-- the quadrumvirate.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, when Mussolini formed his government to go, they called the [INAUDIBLE] a Roma It means they were marching to Rome and to conquer, you know, Italy, he was one of the four people.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
